.. code-block:: pascal

    function TPlayer.switchToWorld(newWorld: integer = 0): boolean;

Switches the TPlayer to the new world (newWorld) via the ingame hop menu. Returns true if successful.
Will choose a random world by default.

.. note::

    - by Clarity
    - Last updated: 09 February 2015 by Clarity

Example:

